  "text": "Human K562 cells were obtained from ATCC and cultured in an IMDM medium containing 10% fetal bovine serum (FBS) and 1% penicillin/streptomycin (P/S). Human HEK293T cells were obtained from ATCC and cultured in a DMEM medium containing 10% FBS and 1% P/S. G1E and G1ER cells were cultured as described [CITATION_1] . All cultures were incubated at 37°C in 5% CO 2 . All cell lines were tested negative for mycoplasma contamination. No cell line used in this study was found in the database of commonly misidentified cell lines maintained by ICLAC and NCBI BioSample.",
